      <title>Vivriti 寻求为新印度私人信贷基金筹集 2.4 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vivriti-seeks-240-million-for-new-india-private-credit-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vivriti Asset Management Pvt. 正在推出一只新的私人信贷基金，用于投资印度中小型公司，进一步利用该资产类别在印度日益增长的受欢迎程度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vivriti-seeks-240-million-for-new-india-private-credit-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:52:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦吉尼斯称欧洲将推迟一年实施银行交易规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/europe-to-delay-bank-trading-rules-by-one-year-mcguinness-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将把全球银行资本规则的一个关键部分推迟一年实施，以便欧盟银行机构不会因美国标准持续争论而遭受不利影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/europe-to-delay-bank-trading-rules-by-one-year-mcguinness-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国十年期国债期货创收盘新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-10-year-bond-futures-see-record-close-amid-bull-run-lxk36470</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管受到当局的严格审查，但中国国债购买狂潮仍在持续，中国主权债券期货周二创下收盘新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-10-year-bond-futures-see-record-close-amid-bull-run-lxk36470</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行聘请丑闻缠身的三菱日联金融集团子公司销售武士债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/hsbc-hires-mufg-unit-to-sell-first-samurai-bond-in-5-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港上海汇丰银行已聘请三菱日联摩根士丹利证券公司作为主承销商，负责销售武士债券。此前，日本发行人因曝光不当商业行为而将该经纪公司排除在交易之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/hsbc-hires-mufg-unit-to-sell-first-samurai-bond-in-5-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行行长警告不要重新设定通胀目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/thai-central-bank-chief-warns-against-tweaking-inflation-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行行长进一步反对政府提高货币当局通胀目标的建议，并指出此举将给东南亚第二大经济体带来风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/thai-central-bank-chief-warns-against-tweaking-inflation-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:48:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政府合作伙伴准备展开内阁之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 准备宣誓就职，但由于 5 月 29 日的选举未能产生绝对胜利者，南非各政党上周同意组成执政联盟，并准备在内阁职位上展开争夺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
